  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The celebrated Memories Off series returns. In a modern setting 10 years after the original series, comes a poignant tale of grief, friendship and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of Junya, lost in his own world but soft-hearted and ready to help those in need, his close friends try to keep him grounded following the tragic loss of his brother. As Junya tries to move forward from his grief, focusing on his studies and his work, he loses himself deep in trying to help others. <br> <br>Whether he's turning a Japanese manor house into a café, or solving the mystery of his brother's death - Junya's life is inexorably linked to the women around him. Only by deepening his relationships with them can he solve their interwoven problems - and through that, find peace himself. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/e9c6013ed8caf9ff469b3f3b8b7eeaea.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/e9c6013ed8caf9ff469b3f3b8b7eeaea.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/906c5ab11921d55a90c6ffb3c41df40b.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/906c5ab11921d55a90c6ffb3c41df40b.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>As you rebuild the Hojo manor, uncover the tangled past and the truth behind Junya’s brother’s death and the mysterious girl who follows you. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/309f86cd983814bf62f7584ee6c81be0.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/309f86cd983814bf62f7584ee6c81be0.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/b2251a8ec60ec3796478dd15d47da486.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/b2251a8ec60ec3796478dd15d47da486.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>Explore different character routes as you foster relationships both old and new, with the five heroines, Chihaya, Hinata, Chunyu, Yuriko and Azusa.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/71ed05fab0590588a1ddcc984243c6cc.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/71ed05fab0590588a1ddcc984243c6cc.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/c3c176655155e295d3271f0c39c0418e.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/c3c176655155e295d3271f0c39c0418e.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>Phenomenal artwork from U35, acclaimed character designer, bringing exquisite production values and unique character creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/70687ef8440ca730dbce3909b6156da9.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/70687ef8440ca730dbce3909b6156da9.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Scenario writing by Tsukasa Tsuchiya, Hiro Akizuki, Rio Izumi, Decocool, Moe Gungu, and Chiyo Yakaku – whose credits include the likes of Steins;Gate 0, Fate/Zero and the Atelier series.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/e2a79ccfb4b2bce9268ce8ac6f12efb4.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/e2a79ccfb4b2bce9268ce8ac6f12efb4.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/b296aa77e8b22169f5f3df22d7c3dd59.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/b296aa77e8b22169f5f3df22d7c3dd59.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/ba314cf5ee893556fbe25257ae310b6a.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/ba314cf5ee893556fbe25257ae310b6a.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>Fully voiced in Japanese, bringing the characters personalities and interactions to life, allowing you to immerse and experience their raw emotion and heartfelt reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/0824314962af5f01af81dd5b48d4cec2.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/0824314962af5f01af81dd5b48d4cec2.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/06a36d0ab9f9979569e41840e882b206.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/06a36d0ab9f9979569e41840e882b206.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>Notable for his work on Steins;Gate, Chaos;Head and the Memories Off series, Takeshi Abo has produced a moving soundtrack which transform this visual novel into a cinematic experience.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The celebrated Memories Off series returns. In a modern setting 10 years after the original series, comes a poignant tale of grief, friendship and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of Junya, lost in his own world but soft-hearted and ready to help those in need, his close friends try to keep him grounded following the tragic loss of his brother. As Junya tries to move forward from his grief, focusing on his studies and his work, he loses himself deep in trying to help others. <br> <br>Whether he's turning a Japanese manor house into a café, or solving the mystery of his brother's death - Junya's life is inexorably linked to the women around him. Only by deepening his relationships with them can he solve their interwoven problems - and through that, find peace himself. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/e9c6013ed8caf9ff469b3f3b8b7eeaea.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/e9c6013ed8caf9ff469b3f3b8b7eeaea.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/906c5ab11921d55a90c6ffb3c41df40b.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/906c5ab11921d55a90c6ffb3c41df40b.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>As you rebuild the Hojo manor, uncover the tangled past and the truth behind Junya’s brother’s death and the mysterious girl who follows you. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline cro