s personalities and interactions to life, allowing you to immerse and experience their raw emotion and heartfelt reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/0824314962af5f01af81dd5b48d4cec2.poster.avif?t=1741788967\" width=600 height=81 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/0824314962af5f01af81dd5b48d4cec2.webm?t=1741788967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras/06a36d0ab9f9979569e41840e882b206.avif?t=1741788967\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838360/extras_big/06a36d0ab9f9979569e41840e882b206.avif?t=1741788967 width=800 height=450 /></span>Notable for his work on Steins;Gate, Chaos;Head and the Memories Off series, Takeshi Abo has produced a moving soundtrack which transform this visual novel into a cinematic experience.</p>",
